ata.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/SCDM/109%2c%e8%a8%b4%2c786%2c20201231%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"SCDM,109,訴,786,20201231,1","JYEAR":"109","JCASE":"訴","JNO":"786","JDATE":"20201231","JTITLE":"違反毒品危害防制條例"}